{
  "stem": "1917.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I became a milkmaid, because I saw there were lots of young guys.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I definitely was interested.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It was an age that I was very interested to be different and to work with guys.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And my sister worked-- we worked for a while in the field picking tomatoes and peanuts.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And Miriam worked in the kitchen, as well as in the farm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But those who worked as milkmaids could stay there all the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They didn't have to be rotated, because you had to learn how to milk the cows.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We went to school half a day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And we learned Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I learned Hebrew very fast.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "In three months, I could speak Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And then in 1952, we were drafted into the Israeli Army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Up to that time, I did not really feel very different because in that [NON-ENGLISH] village, there were children from 30 countries.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I learned to say I love you in 10 languages.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And we all were children who have been traumatized in one way or another by World War II.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "But once I was in the Israeli Army, there  were young people-- soldiers, women-- who  had families in Tel Aviv, who could home after finishing work, or on weekends.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I had no place to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And that became very difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, Miriam and I got separated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She studied to become a nurse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because one of my cousins said, well, you know, growing up as a man, I look at it that for any man is difficult to deal with one woman.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How are they going to deal with two of them alike?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you ought to go your different ways-- separate ways.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she started to become a nurse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went to the engineering corps.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
